e":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5686e4473d0aa9b9da6a17c7f9528aa44ce4b02","tid":1990444,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:54:00.000Z","msg":"直選就算奇蹟66443,都係23<br />\n功能組別區一加超區都係4,其他有把握都係7席<br />\n23+4+7都係34<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T17:10:43.000Z","msg":"其實又唔係咁悲<br />\n依家民主派有6席 另外dq左嘅姚松炎+陳醫生<br />\n加埋進攻飲食業/進出口<br />\n<br />\n不過我諗35+都係會被dq"},{"pid":"84fe93972f5a2556ba951ad9d80a731a1ff27db8","tid":1990444,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T17:15:04.000Z","msg":"我個老師，退休好幾年<br />\n成日屌中共，親台灣，都幾黃<br />\n佢話幾廿歲人唔會移民<br />\n但佢無遊行，仲日日去藍店飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連選民都從未登記過<br />\n我勸極唔掂"},{"pid":"e360f703bcbed790869c675b6bbc51ef2d768fbb","tid":1990444,"uid":83609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84fe93972f5a2556ba951ad9d80a731a1ff27db8","tid":1990444,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T17:15:04.000Z","msg":"我個老師，退休好幾年<br />\n成日屌中共，親台灣，都幾黃<br />\n佢話幾廿歲人唔會移民<br />\n但佢無遊行，仲日日去藍店飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連選民都從未登記過<br />\n我勸極唔掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T17:50:50.000Z","msg":"佢想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢個人好矛盾下"},{"pid":"d27a2fb3cb579f852d8f86d12c4e7c46429e2d05","tid":1990444,"uid":277381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:58:07.000Z","msg":"其實好似台灣咁，好似唔駛做選民投票都有得投票，點解香港咁麻煩，要登記先有得投 。有冇同感"}]}